snippet.title: Cute Fames Adventure (Final Trailer)
snippet.description:
Fame: "It's Been Awhile, Hasn't it.?"
Lee: "I bet you've missed us, But it's time we finish our journey."

This is the final trailer for Cute Fames Adventure.
Releasing August 24th on, Steam And Google Play Store.
(Wishlist when the steam page is online!)

This game has been a long time coming, And i'm glad to finish it with you all, By departing it onto more platforms then one, This will be the first game, Of a long series, And only you can show your support on these next games, With this first one.
- Fame/CuteFame.

Links:
https://www.addevent.com/event/hT22572380 (Calender Event)
https://cutefame.net (Main Website)
